1
00:00:10,933.3329999999987 --> 117:36:50,933.3330000042915
[g@Wukong was furious.

2
117:38:30,933.3330000042915 --> 215:13:30,933.3329999446869
"The Bull Demon King tricked me!"@g]

3
215:15:10,933.3329999446869 --> 388:33:30,933.3329999446869
The monkey rushed back to the cave and smashed the door. [i@Crash!@i]

4
388:35:10,933.3329999446869 --> 475:56:50,933.3329999446869
The Bull Demon King ran outside.

5
475:58:30,933.3329999446869 --> 638:08:30,933.3330001831055
"You villain!" he shouted. "You destroyed my door!"

6
638:10:10,933.3330001831055 --> 734:00:10,933.3330001831055
"Give me that fan right now!" yelled Wukong.

7
734:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 832:03:30,933.3330001831055
"Or I'll destroy the rest of your mountain!"

8
832:05:10,933.3330001831055 --> 938:50:10,933.3330001831055
"Never!" said the demon.

9
938:51:50,933.3330001831055 --> 1052:16:50,933.3330001831055
Wukong charged toward the demon.

10
1052:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1170:18:30,933.3330001831055
[i@Poof!@i] The demon turned into a crane and flew away.

11
1170:20:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1328:41:50,933.3330001831055
"He's not the only one who can turn into other animals," thought the monkey.

12
1328:43:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1487:16:50,933.3330001831055
Wukong turned into a phoenix and shot after the crane.

13
1487:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1590:25:10,933.3330001831055
With his claws out, he swooped down at the crane.

14
1590:26:50,933.3330001831055 --> 1694:23:30,933.3330001831055
The crane dipped lower and Wukong missed.

15
1694:25:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1801:41:50,933.3330001831055
When Wukong looked back, the crane was gone.

16
1801:43:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1871:00:10,933.3330001831055
"Where did he go?" thought Wukong.

17
1871:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2035:18:30,933.3330001831055
He looked down and saw an antelope grazing in a field. "That's him!"

18
2035:20:10,933.3330001831055 --> 2125:25:10,933.3330001831055
[g@Wukong landed and turned into a tiger.

19
2125:26:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2228:35:10,933.3330001831055
He crept through the tall grass.@g]

20
2228:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2351:25:10,933.3330001831055
When he got close to the antelope, he leaped.

21
2351:26:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2514:25:10,933.3330001831055
Light flashed, and the antelope turned into a huge white bull.

22
2514:26:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2641:23:30,933.3330001831055
The bull flew up into the sky, and Wukong followed.

23
2641:25:10,933.3330001831055 --> 2740:36:50,933.3330001831055
He had almost caught up to the bull, when he heard a shout.

24
2740:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2815:41:50,933.3330001831055
[g@"Stand back, Wukong!"

25
2815:43:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2886:00:10,933.3330001831055
It was a soldier from Heaven.@g]

26
2886:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2971:50:10,933.3330001831055
"The Jade Emperor sent us to help you."

27
2971:51:50,933.3330001831055 --> 3057:00:10,933.3330001831055
More soldiers rushed toward the bull.

28
3057:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 3170:35:10,933.3330001831055
With a snort, the bull spun around and flew the other way.

29
3170:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 3292:13:30,933.3330001831055
But other soldiers appeared and blocked the bull's path.

30
3292:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 3398:48:30,933.3330001831055
Wukong watched as soldiers surrounded the bull.

31
3398:50:10,933.3330001831055 --> 3586:06:50,933.3330001831055
They moved in closer, their swords and spears all pointed at the bull.

32
3586:08:30,933.3330001831055 --> 3692:16:50,933.3330001831055
[g@The Bull Demon King returned to his demon form.

33
3692:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 3785:18:30,933.3330001831055
"Please, don't hurt me!"@g]

34
3785:20:10,933.3330001831055 --> 3877:51:50,933.3330001831055
The Iron Immortal was rushing toward the soldiers.

35
3877:53:30,933.3330001831055 --> 3952:23:30,933.3330001831055
[g@"Don't harm my husband!" she cried.

36
3952:25:10,933.3330001831055 --> 4026:35:10,933.3330001831055
"He didn't mean to be evil!"@g]

37
4026:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 4092:58:30,933.3330001831055
One soldier lowered his sword.

38
4093:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 4181:35:10,933.3330001831055
"We won't harm you if you're truly sorry for being evil.

39
4181:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 4296:11:50,933.3330001831055
But right now you're stopping the Tang Monk from continuing his journey.

40
4296:13:30,933.3330001831055 --> 4371:15:10,933.3330001831055
Sun Wukong needs your fan."

41
4371:16:50,933.3330001831055 --> 4477:40:10,933.3330001831055
The Iron Immortal handed the fan to the soldier.

42
4477:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 4535:51:50,933.3330001831055
[g@"Here's the fan," she said.

43
4535:53:30,933.3330001831055 --> 4596:21:50,933.3330001831055
"We are truly sorry.@g]

44
4596:23:30,933.3330001831055 --> 4687:58:30,933.3330001831055
My husband and I will be good Buddhists from now on.

45
4688:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 4766:21:50,933.3330001831055
Just please, don't hurt us."

46
4766:23:30,933.3330001831055 --> 4849:10:10,933.3330001831055
The soldier looked at the Bull Demon King.

47
4849:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 4957:58:30,933.3330001831055
The demon nodded. "We promise."

48
4958:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 5038:46:50,933.3330001831055
[g@"Very well," said the soldier.

49
5038:48:30,933.3330001831055 --> 5109:18:30,933.3330001831055
"You two may return to your cave.@g]

50
5109:20:10,933.3330001831055 --> 5192:26:50,933.3330001831055
But you must stay out of trouble from now on."

51
5192:28:30,933.3330001831055 --> 5309:33:30,933.3330001831055
The demon and his wife bowed and left.

52
5309:35:10,933.3330001831055 --> 5419:31:50,933.3330001831055
The soldier handed the fan to Wukong.

53
5419:33:30,933.3330001831055 --> 5533:16:50,933.3330001831055
"It's good that you'll be the one to put out [n@the Mountain of Flames, Wukong."

54
5533:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 5638:35:10,933.3330001831055
Wukong was confused. "Why?"

55
5638:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 5825:08:30,933.3330001831055
"You're the one who caused the fire," said the soldier.

56
5825:10:10,933.3330001831055 --> 5912:36:50,933.3330001831055
"It was when Laozi tried to burn you up in his pot.

57
5912:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6035:16:50,933.3330001831055
You leaped out of the pot, disturbing the fire in his workroom.

58
6035:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6168:13:30,933.3330001831055
A burning ember fell to Earth that day and [n@started the fire on the mountain."

59
6168:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6226:43:30,933.3330001831055
[g@Wukong looked at the fan.

60
6226:45:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6346:33:30,933.3330001831055
"I'll be happy to put out the fire."@g]

61
6346:35:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6424:06:50,933.3330001831055
Wukong returned to the village.

62
6424:08:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6542:00:10,933.3330001831055
The Tang Monk and his companions were at the old man's house again.

63
6542:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 6670:33:30,933.3330001831055
Once again they thanked the man and followed the road up the hill.

64
6670:35:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6778:35:10,933.3330001831055
At the top they looked at the Mountain of Flames.

65
6778:36:50,933.3330001831055 --> 6925:58:30,933.3330001831055
Wukong lifted the fan and waved it. [i@Whoosh!@i]

66
6926:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 7012:38:30,933.3330001831055
Instantly the fire went out.

67
7012:40:10,933.3330001831055 --> 7184:10:10,933.3330001831055
The air cooled down, and Wukong saw the valley start to turn green.

68
7184:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7345:15:10,933.3330001831055
Leaves grew on trees, and small flowers popped up here and there.

69
7345:16:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7480:05:10,933.3330001831055
Birds sang in the branches as other animals ran through the grass.

70
7480:06:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7531:50:10,933.3330001831055
[g@Wukong smiled.

71
7531:51:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7616:08:30,933.3330001831055
He had done evil things a long time ago.@g]

72
7616:10:10,933.3330001831055 --> 7801:46:50,933.3330001831055
Now he was fixing them.

